title: Jennifer Lopez Wears Incredible Bodysuit With Blingy Emoji Prayer Hands
text: Jennifer Lopez Wears Incredible Bodysuit With Blingy Emoji Prayer Hands Getty By Alyssa Bailey Feb 9, 2017 Jennifer Lopez, forever #bodygoals, shared a first look at her new glitzy bodysuit for her Las Vegas show last night. It's from The Blonds and is basically blinged-out prayer emoji hands praising a holy amount of cleavage: A photo posted by Jennifer Lopez (@jlo) on Feb 9, 2017 at 1:32am PST Advertisement - Continue Reading Below
